00:39:51,936 --> 00:39:54,616
tiga bulan lagi.

966
00:39:56,136 --> 00:39:56,936
Profesor Ren,

967
00:39:57,297 --> 00:39:58,656
jujur ​​saja padaku.

968
00:39:59,136 --> 00:40:01,176
Orang-orang mengatakan kepada saya bahwa jika praktisi TCM

969
00:40:01,577 --> 00:40:02,577
